*[[poke]]
*[[stab]]
*[[strike]]

====Example usages====
*But that first night he gently took me to bed and '''caressed''' and kissed me - not the approximation or imitation of lovemaking, but the real thing, ending in a physical connection that I had no inkling was possible between men. - From ''The Blue Star'' in ''Violet Quill'', Robert Ferro
*''She loves being caressed by her boyfriend.'''

